linearLowerLimit.title: Linear lower limit
linearLowerLimit.description: Lower linear constraint in the local space of this entity.

linearUpperLimit.title: Linear upper limit
linearUpperLimit.description: Upper linear constraint in the local space of this entity.

angularLowerLimit.title: Angular lower limit
angularLowerLimit.description: Lower angular constraint in the local space of this entity.

angularUpperLimit.title: Angular upper limit
angularUpperLimit.description: Upper angular constraint in the local space of this entity.

enableCollision.title: Enable Collision
enableCollision.description: Enable collision between linked rigid bodies.

pivotA.title: Pivot
pivotA.description: Position of the constraint in the local space of this entity.

axisA.title: Axis
axisA.description: Axis of rotation of the constraint in the local space this entity.

pivotB.title: Connected Pivot
pivotB.description: Position of the constraint in the local space of the connected entity (if specified).

axisB.title: Connected Axis
axisB.description: Axis of rotation of the constraint in the local space of the connected entity (if specified).

limits.title: Limits
limits.description: Low and high angular limits for the constraint in degrees. By default, low is greater than high meaning no limits.

softness.title: Softness
softness.description: Softness of the constraint. Recommend 0.8 to 1. Describes the percentage of limits where movement is free. Beyond this softness percentage, the limit is gradually enforced until the "hard" (1.0) limit is reached.

biasFactor.title: Bias Factor
biasFactor.description: Bias factor of the constraint. Recommend 0.3 +/- approximately 0.3. Strength with which constraint resists zeroth order (angular, not angular velocity) limit violation.

relaxationFactor.title: Relaxation Factor
relaxationFactor.description: Relaxation factor of the constraint. Recommend to keep this near 1. The lower the value, the less the constraint will fight velocities which violate the angular limits.

enableMotor.title: Use Motor
enableMotor.description: Enable a motor to power the automatic rotation around the hinge axis.

breakingThreshold.title: Break Threshold
breakingThreshold.description: Maximum breaking impulse threshold required to break the constraint.

enableCollision.title: Enable Collision
enableCollision.description: Enable collision between linked rigid bodies.

debugRender.title: Debug Render
debugRender.description: Enable to render a representation of the constraint.

debugColor.title: Debug Color
debugColor.description: The color of the debug rendering of the constraint.
